                from day one? Are you flexible to be based anywhere in the world for at least a few years? This trainee program is run by 
                our Expansion and Global sales functions and has been created to develop future leaders. The Expansion and Global sales 
                functions focus on finding new locations, create the best possible shopping experience, maximize the sales and run profitable stores.
                <br />
                <br />
