                entire value chain of our products from design to production, buying and sales? Do you want to develop in the area of business 
                controlling and analysis within our Head office functions where your decisions will affect H&M globally? The Business trainee
                program is created to develop future leaders with a great passion for business and creating the best customer offer.
                <br />
                <br />
